RimuHosting,specializes,in,Linux,Virtual,Private,Server,hosting,plans,providing,subscribed,users,with,a,choice,of,Linux,distributions,SSH,root,access,and,dedicated,Linus,sysadmin,support,The,RimuHosting,API,is,especially,useful,for,users,who,have,a,domain,name,that,points,to,a,changing,IP,address,The,DNS,API,allows,users,to,change,a,domain,s,IP,address,automate,the,setup,and,changing,of,mail,servers,and,text,records,delete,records,and,more,An,account,with,service,and,an,API,key,are,required,to,use,this,service